Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.cell.data

Enum SimulationData

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SimulationData>
      • org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.cell.data.SimulationData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SimulationData>
    public enum SimulationData
extends Enum<SimulationData>
    SimulationData Singleton that manages all dynamic simulation data from MOSAIC. It includes:
    • the current simulation time
    • the position of each known node
    • the vehicle speeds (rsus, tl, cs have a speed of 0)
